round": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1888272227746707403"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIs7rmj5Psv79DEAMaCTExNDE4MzgxMiDtgI+/BjAAOLEDQA9yEzE4ODgyNzIyMjc3NDY3MDc0MDN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1743046025.13014", "card_id": "Q_542076156", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 795}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《潜伏》李涯很能干，为什么站长却更喜欢余则成？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-5fe2de716b949feb92d4f14029a6f8db_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "91 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/542076156"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Is7rmj5Psv79DEAMaCDgyNzQzMjY2IO2Ym5YGMAA47A1AEHIJNTQyMDc2MTU2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1743046025.13470", "card_id": "Q_15488860668", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 50}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何证明你是《炉石传说》的老玩家？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-39291d0f2817e04929c7b05a69226856_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "90 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/15488860668"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIs7rmj5Psv79DEAMaCTExNDA5ODc0NyD1vvS+BjAAOC1AEXILMTU0ODg4NjA2Njh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1743046025.13861", "card_id": "Q_665731716", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 17}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么 transformer 的 FFN 需要先升维再降维？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "W_2 矩阵一般是 4d\\times d 的，那么它的 rank 最高为 d，也就是说至少有 3d 行可以被其他行线性表出，假设某个 inputx\\in R^{1\\times d} 在经过 W_1 以及激活函数后的 hidden state 为 h\\in R^{1\\times 4d} 那么 FFN 的 outputh\\cdot W_2 可以看作是对 W_2 的 4d 行进行一个加权求和 \\sum_{i=1}^{4d}{h_i}W_{2,i}，其中 h_i 代表 h 的第 i 个分量，W_{2,i} 代表 W_2 的第 i 行。由于 W_2 的低秩特性，我总可以在 W_2 找到 n(n\\leq d) 个线性无关的行 (假设就是前 n 行)，从而对于任意 1\\leq i\\leq 4d，W_{2,i} 都可以由这 n 行线性表出 W_{2,i}=\\sum_{j=1}^{n}{c_j}W_{2,j}，所以上述加权求和总可以进行改写：\\sum_{i=1}^{4d}{h_i}W_{2,i}=\\sum_{i=1}^{n}{k_i}W_{2,i}，那么 W_2 矩阵只需要这 n 行即可，模型只需要学习到如何通过 W_1 和激活函数来得到「新的」h'\\in R^{1\\times n}=\\{k_1, k_2,...,k_n\\}，那么这么看完全不需要现在的 FFN 中先升维再降维的操作，所以为什么降低 FFN 中矩阵的维度实践中往往效果会变差呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-b7ade636138b3d7a3dab6ba84f3e95c6_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "85 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/665731716"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIs7rmj5Psv79DEAMaCTExMDIxNzk0OCC51ca2BjAAOPsBQBJyCTY2NTczMTcxNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1743046025.15470", "card_id": "Q_15238304263", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "网传苹果将出超薄新版手机，iPhone 17 Air 或是苹果首款无端口手机，这一改变有哪些意义？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "苹果即将在今年 9 月发布 iPhone 17 智能手机系列，而从目前透出的消息来看，苹果似乎将「更轻、更薄、更简洁」视为产品重点。 科技评论员 Sonny Dickson 最新在 X 上发布了 iPhone 17 的四款原型机图片，一般苹果的外壳和配件制造商会使用这些版本来为手机制造做准备。其中，市场传言的 iPhone 17 Air 尤其引人瞩目，因其厚度明显较其他版本轻薄。 iPhone 17 Air 的厚度预计将只有 5.5 毫米，背面只有一个摄像头，就像 iPhone 16E 一样。此外，这款新加入的 Air 手机似乎将是一款 6.6 英寸的手机，这也被苹果的资深报道记者马克·古尔曼所证实。 古尔曼补充称，苹果曾考虑将 17 Air 设计为 6.9 英寸的手机，即与 16 Pro Max 尺寸一致，但后来担心带有大屏幕的超薄设备容易弯曲，最后放弃了这一计划。 另一大关于 17 Air 的重大革新在于，古尔曼声称该机型可能将是苹果的首款无端口手机，即充电方式仅保留无线充电，所有数据同步都通过云端完成。 不过，古尔曼也提醒，苹果可能最终会放弃无端口计划，因为该公司担忧欧洲监管部门可以用 Type C 端口的规定来限制无端口设计。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-043a579e597d01bebb3091123891e4bd_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "75 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/15238304263"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIs7rmj5Psv79DEAMaCTExNDAzMzQwNyCu6OK+BjAAOBpAE3ILMTUyMzgzMDQyNjN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1743046025.16803", "card_id": "Q_14566518355", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "研究生复试时是否要向导师表示你对某个理论或领域特别熟悉？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-36c122f1fa4ba3c869c1daeebac83274_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "72 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/14566518355"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIs7rmj5Psv79DEAMaCTExMzg5MDAzOSCQwrm+BjAAOBtAFHILMTQ1NjY1MTgzNTV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1743046025.17088", "card_id": "Q_12920490784", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 134}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "哪个瞬间，你感觉被孩子一句话就治愈了？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-720bebb1f099618221746a17df44f4ac_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "61 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/12920490784"}